question: Koh-chài bô-sī multi-task ê model tit-tio̍h siōng-kē ê liân-sòa Mean Squared Error (MSE_over)?
Chhiūⁿ-chòe ēng "Multi-Task" chhiam-chèng ê só͘-ū model ê MSE7 (7-kang ê horizon) ê pâi-kin-sòan-tōa?
Tī tē-jī ê MSE3 ê tâi-ê (tē-jī siōng-pháiⁿ ê) model lâi-kóng, i ê MSE30 ê tâi-ê sī án-chóaⁿ-iūⁿ?
HTML模型佇预测地平（prediction horizon）从3天延长到30天，其平均平方误差（MSE）的趋势是按怎？预测的准确度（predictive accuracy）随着时间有进步抑是退步？
answer: HTML模型的预测准确度（predictive accuracy）随着预测地平（prediction horizon）的延长而进步。其MSE值从MSE3（0.845）一贯下降到MSE7（0.349）、MSE15（0.251），最后到MSE30（0.158），这表示误差减少，所以对较长期的预测表现更好。

question: Thài-tāi êMODELê，hō͘ lâng-lâng khòaⁿ-māi bô sī "Multi-Task" ê， koh-ū MSE15 ê sió-kó͘ lóng sī 0.31 í-hā ê, chin chhiáⁿ kā in lóng lia̍h chhut-lâi.
Kui-í bô-tāi-chāi sī siáⁿ-chi̍t ê bô-tāi-chāi, i ê MSE ê siaⁿ-chè lóng pí pa̍t-ê koân, thang thiah-ha̍k i ê chha-su?
answer: GPT-3.5-Turbo bô-tāi-chāi sī chi̍t ê chin chhut-thâu ê bô-tāi-chāi. I ê MSE siaⁿ-chè chiap-pà só͘-ū ê tio̍h-sî-kan (MSE_over: 2.198, MSE3: 2.152, MSE7: 1.793, MSE15: 2.514, MSE30: 2.332) koh pí pa̍t-ê bô-tāi-chāi lóng chin koân, chē-chē bô-tāi-chāi ê MSE siaⁿ-chè sī khah-kē hō͘ 1.0. Che piáu-sī i ê chiap-lio̍k-lêng pí pa̍t-ê bô-tāi-chāi lóng chin chha-su.

question: Thong-koà chin-chiâⁿ ê MSE3 ê kui-lūi choân-pō͘ lêng-chí lóng sī tùi GPT-3.5-Turbo lêng-chí lâi ê toā-sió sī sì-píⁿ? Chiong hôe-tap chòe píng-lē, lūn tio̍h chi̍t ê sió-sió ê píng-lē.
Nā-sī RiskLabs model ê MSE_over nā-sī chham 25% khah hó (tō-sī kám-chió 25%), i ê sin chi̍t-ê kè-ta̍t ē sī siáⁿ-mih, chi̍h chham HTML model ê MSE_over pí-kàu, ē sī siáⁿ-mih pâi?
answer: RiskLabs ê sin MSE_over ē-sī 0.243. Chit-ê kè-ta̍t pí HTML model ê MSE_over 0.401 khah kē, só͘-í koh khah hó.

question: Tùi chiat-chāu lâi-kóan, model hō͘ phiau-chòe 'Multi-Task' kah ū 'VaR' sêng-chek ê liân-chāp cháiⁿ-iūⁿ?
answer: Ū chi̍t ê khò-kò͘ ê koan-liân. Kāng-chi̍t ê model hō͘ phiau-chòe 'Multi-Task' (GPT-3.5-Turbo kah RiskLabs) chiah ū kì-lio̍k ê sò͘-ba̍k-sè 'VaR' sêng-chek. Koh-ū, m̄-sī só͘-ū 'Multi-Task' model lóng ū VaR sêng-chek (chhiūⁿ HTML), koh m̄-sī ū chi̍t ê hui-'Multi-Task' model ū i ê sêng-chek, che sī chí-sīnav-khì-lâi ê ki-su̍t sī chi̍t ê chin-chē tī 'Multi-Task' model ê cheng-chi̍t ê tiâu-bo̍k tī che ê chu-liāu-khò͘.

question: Lé-khuán ê hêng-iàⁿ-chiāu liám-chāu ê khut-á ū hui-sò͘-jī ê tū-chāi-chiau jī-bó, chiūⁿ hō͘ lé-khuán ê lūi sī chiah-ê bô māi ê?
answer: ʻVaRʻ ê khut-á ū hui-sò͘-jī ê jī-bó ('/'). Chiah-ê jī-bó sī bô māi ê lūi sī: Classical Method, LSTM, MT-LSTM-ATT, HAN, MRDM, kap HTML.

question: Nai khuann kiat-kó (MSE3 sí-kàu MSE30) kah hû-hiám phòe-kè (VaR) lóng siōng-hó ê sî, nai khuann sī chún-sî chòe-chiap?
answer: Chòe-chiap ê liâm-tūi kah kòe-khì ê suan-su̍t-koân (MSE) ê phòe-kè sī siōng-koân ê liâm-tūi, kah siōng-koân ê hû-hiám phòe-kè (VaR) sī 0.049, chia̍h-chòe chin-chiap ê kòe-khì ê suan-su̍t-koân kah khò-sìn ê hû-hiám phòe-kè.
